[[Image:Marston Hall, Engineering, UMass, Amherst MA.jpg|thumb|right|250px|<center>Marston Hall</center>]] '''Marston Hall''' is an academic building on the campus of the [[University of Massachusetts Amherst]]. It houses the Dean of Engineering and parts of the Departments of Civil and Environmental Engineering, Mechanical and Industrial Engineering, and Electrical and Computer Engineering.
